      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，下班回来先下楼，这个很轻松，5分。最后坐下休息，也是5分，完美结束一天。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Go downstairs: 5: Me",
